intro: Wondering who made this?  If you can help?  We'd love for you to join us.
pageBody:
This project started as a collaboration between the founders of Insight Fit, Lead Robot, and Sigma Digital.We all felt the need to act, and to contribute.  Reach out to our collective networks, we found that many others were excited to do something that could help during the COVID 19 global  crisis.
